responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "C0BD7A614151201F632EC8B711C65094", "It is time for you to know our role. Your gift of the bones of the innocent proves your path is our path. We are the the Idolaters. We are those that serve the shackled Priestess of Pain and Suffering. Together we shall release her and usher in the fall of this wretched realm.")
